me/h0036","IconName":"h0036s4_sp2","IconLocate":2,"Text":"C, chat?","sfxName":"h0036_story_016","sfxVolume":1.0},{"ID":"char_h0036_002_dialog_english##_20_003","SpeakerName":"Lisa","SpeakerAssetName":"CharacterName/h0036","IconName":"h0036s4_happiness","IconLocate":2,"Text":"Of course you can.
